WEBVTT

01:39.479 --> 01:43.670
[Road to Success]

01:44.520 --> 01:47.840
[Episode 7]

01:48.950 --> 01:51.350
I wonder if you've ever heard of

01:51.350 --> 01:53.710
Edward Hall's theory of personal space.

01:54.150 --> 01:55.080
What do you mean?

01:57.950 --> 01:59.430
I mean,

01:59.430 --> 02:00.830
given your personality,

02:01.070 --> 02:03.270
you normally keep people at a distance.

02:03.510 --> 02:05.680
But you're standing
so close to me right now.

02:05.680 --> 02:07.880
It's beyond what's considered normal.

02:11.910 --> 02:13.590
If I'm not mistaken,

02:13.610 --> 02:14.730
Wen,

02:14.800 --> 02:16.030
since you went out of your way

02:16.030 --> 02:17.150
to stop me from being the supervisor,

02:17.150 --> 02:19.150
you don't want the team regrouped, do you?

02:19.150 --> 02:20.470
If you hadn't come,

02:20.470 --> 02:22.710
the football team wouldn't have regrouped.

02:22.710 --> 02:23.680
Re...

02:25.630 --> 02:27.360
Aren't you a transfer student?

02:28.079 --> 02:29.400
Or is it that

02:29.840 --> 02:30.910
there's someone on the football team

02:30.910 --> 02:32.680
you particularly hate?

02:34.520 --> 02:36.150
I don't have to tell you.

02:40.400 --> 02:41.190
Fine.

02:41.910 --> 02:43.310
Anyway,

02:43.310 --> 02:44.570
whoever it is you hate,

02:44.910 --> 02:47.240
I suggest you just join the football team.

02:47.400 --> 02:48.280
That way,

02:48.280 --> 02:49.630
you can piss him off every day

02:49.630 --> 02:50.840
and enjoy

02:50.840 --> 02:52.840
the thrill of annoying him up close.

02:54.470 --> 02:56.870
You still want me
to join the football team.

02:57.720 --> 02:59.440
Why should I listen to you?

03:04.400 --> 03:07.030
Kids have such hot tempers now.

03:12.120 --> 03:14.230
How could they just leave

03:14.470 --> 03:16.520
something so heavy at the door?

03:16.870 --> 03:18.400
The peacocks fly southeast.

03:18.400 --> 03:20.310
-Peacock flying southeast.
-Peacock flying southeast.

03:20.310 --> 03:21.750
Ms. Lin is here.

03:22.750 --> 03:24.560
You came just in time. Help me.

03:24.560 --> 03:26.310
-Qin, take that in.
-Okay.

03:28.120 --> 03:28.750
Slow down, Lu.

03:28.750 --> 03:30.000
Boss, you're strong.

03:30.000 --> 03:30.750
Of course.

03:32.520 --> 03:32.960
Ms. Lin,

03:32.960 --> 03:34.030
where should we put this?

03:34.030 --> 03:35.030
Just put it here.

03:39.590 --> 03:42.150
What brings you here?

03:47.190 --> 03:48.030
Ms. Lin,

03:48.310 --> 03:49.190
um...

03:49.510 --> 03:51.829
do you know why we only listen to Fu?

03:55.120 --> 03:56.140
I know.

03:56.430 --> 03:58.079
If a person in a team

03:58.079 --> 03:59.520
is always giving

03:59.520 --> 04:01.310
and doing the hardest things,

04:01.310 --> 04:03.570
of course, you'd be afraid of losing him.

04:05.630 --> 04:07.240
How do you know everything?

04:07.240 --> 04:08.080
You're no fun.

04:09.800 --> 04:11.360
You're here for Fu Xinshu?

04:11.360 --> 04:12.190
Ms. Lin,

04:12.360 --> 04:13.910
can you help us tell Fu Xinshu

04:13.910 --> 04:16.240
about the extra practice this afternoon?

04:16.870 --> 04:18.920
Lying is not good.

04:20.480 --> 04:21.390
How about this?

04:21.390 --> 04:22.870
The three of us will take turns

04:22.870 --> 04:24.930
cleaning the equipment room for you.

04:25.120 --> 04:26.120
Deal.

04:27.480 --> 04:28.240
First, help me

04:28.240 --> 04:30.000
sort out the things in the box.

04:30.240 --> 04:33.190
There isn't trash
waiting for us, is there?

04:41.830 --> 04:43.310
New uniforms!

04:43.310 --> 04:45.240
Ms. Lin, are you giving these to us?

04:46.950 --> 04:47.790
Remember to lock the door.

04:47.790 --> 04:49.040
Thank you, Ms. Lin!

04:51.040 --> 04:51.950
This is quite cool.

04:51.950 --> 04:54.010
We won't be charged for this, will we?

04:57.560 --> 04:59.630
Didn't they notify me of extra practice?

04:59.630 --> 05:00.690
Where is everyone?

05:04.800 --> 05:06.110
No bags either.

05:06.270 --> 05:07.670
Are they messing with me?

05:09.160 --> 05:09.950
Fu.

05:22.560 --> 05:23.890
What are you guys doing?

05:24.650 --> 05:25.650
Bro,

05:25.680 --> 05:27.500
I'm the eagle on the pitch.

05:27.750 --> 05:29.540
I'm Lin Lu, following the Boss.

05:29.600 --> 05:30.890
No. 15, Zheng Ren,

05:30.920 --> 05:32.250
the god of the midfield.

05:32.600 --> 05:33.740
I'm Qi Liang.

05:33.840 --> 05:34.770
In the backcourt,

05:34.770 --> 05:36.030
I shine the brightest.

05:36.240 --> 05:37.430
The flying fried skewer,

05:37.430 --> 05:39.040
the sweeper on the pitch.

05:39.040 --> 05:40.920
I'm the god of speed on the pitch,

05:40.920 --> 05:42.240
the real Flash!

05:42.270 --> 05:43.790
I'm No. 7, Chen Jianghe.

05:43.870 --> 05:45.490
Scoring goals is my destiny.

05:45.680 --> 05:47.000
I'm No. 1, Feng Suo!

05:47.310 --> 05:48.920
I'm everyone's safe haven!

05:48.920 --> 05:50.480
I'm No. 23, Zhi Hui.

05:50.680 --> 05:51.890
I had my fortune read.

05:52.120 --> 05:53.310
We will always

05:53.310 --> 05:54.750
play football together!

06:20.360 --> 06:21.700
I'm No. 10, Fu Xinshu!

06:22.630 --> 06:24.690
I want to win games with everyone

06:24.710 --> 06:25.970
and become champions!

06:26.630 --> 06:27.870
You still remember.

06:28.310 --> 06:29.800
You must keep your word.

06:31.430 --> 06:32.240
Let's go!

06:33.870 --> 06:35.950
-Let's go!
-Let's go!

06:38.350 --> 06:41.340
♪ Even if no one cheers ♪

06:40.360 --> 06:41.630
-Come on, Fu!
-Come on, Fu!

06:41.630 --> 06:42.720
Fu, go!

06:42.260 --> 06:44.830
♪ I'll keep fighting my way through ♪

06:42.720 --> 06:43.659
-Fu!
-Fu!

06:43.680 --> 06:45.159
Go, go!

06:46.310 --> 06:48.070
♪ On a deserted battlefield ♪

06:46.430 --> 06:47.890
Don't panic! Don't panic!

06:48.800 --> 06:50.250
♪ I grow stronger
with a resounding voice ♪

06:50.780 --> 06:53.970
♪ I'll take every scar ♪

06:54.550 --> 06:58.270
♪ As my badge of honor ♪

06:55.430 --> 06:57.560
What do you say? What do you say?

06:57.560 --> 06:58.630
Take off!

07:11.220 --> 07:14.490
♪ If facing every storm is ♪

07:14.970 --> 07:18.210
♪ What it takes to grow ♪

07:17.270 --> 07:18.560
Boss, pass it to me, Boss!

07:18.560 --> 07:19.240
Pass it to me! Pass it to me!

07:19.060 --> 07:21.800
♪ I will stubbornly
go against the current ♪

07:19.830 --> 07:20.630
Boss, come on!

07:20.630 --> 07:22.090
Pass it to me! Pass it to me!

07:22.190 --> 07:23.920
Boss, pass it to me! Pass it to me!

07:22.600 --> 07:25.330
♪ And let myself go wild ♪

07:26.320 --> 07:29.410
♪ No matter how long the road ahead ♪

07:30.530 --> 07:32.790
♪ Nothing can stop me ♪

07:32.870 --> 07:34.360
These kids are not losers.

07:34.290 --> 07:35.820
♪ Break through every haze of doubt ♪

07:35.120 --> 07:36.050
On the contrary,

07:36.240 --> 07:37.560
they are sincere,

07:36.570 --> 07:38.120
♪ Chase the light within me ♪

07:37.560 --> 07:38.510
passionate,

07:38.510 --> 07:39.560
and loyal.

07:39.010 --> 07:41.670
♪ Strong wings grow through the storm ♪

07:39.870 --> 07:41.930
They have countless shining points.

07:42.320 --> 07:45.330
♪ Even if no one cheers ♪

07:43.360 --> 07:45.360
They deserve to be treated better.

07:45.830 --> 07:47.360
Maybe returning to the pitch

07:46.240 --> 07:48.680
♪ I'll keep fighting my way through ♪

07:47.360 --> 07:49.360
can help them get through the bottleneck

07:49.360 --> 07:50.560
and reinvent themselves.

07:50.290 --> 07:52.220
♪ On a deserted battlefield ♪

07:52.770 --> 07:54.350
♪ I grow stronger
with a resounding voice ♪

07:54.760 --> 07:58.070
♪ I'll take every scar ♪

07:57.920 --> 07:58.560
Come on!

07:58.520 --> 08:02.010
♪ As my badge of honor ♪

08:04.510 --> 08:05.360
Nice shot!

08:06.480 --> 08:08.600
Boys, come and have some drinks!

08:10.240 --> 08:11.120
-Thank you, Ms. Lin.
-Thank you, Ms. Lin.

08:11.120 --> 08:12.430
-Ms. Lin.
-Ms. Lin.

08:13.190 --> 08:13.750
I'll distribute them.
I'll distribute them.

08:13.750 --> 08:15.040
Come here. Come here.

08:15.800 --> 08:16.750
Ms. Lin.

08:16.750 --> 08:17.610
Let me tell you.

08:17.750 --> 08:18.920
We're against Lyujing soon.

08:18.920 --> 08:20.120
We can definitely win.

08:20.120 --> 08:20.680
But Ms. Lin,

08:20.680 --> 08:22.270
aren't we still short one player?

08:22.270 --> 08:23.160
Don't worry.

08:23.160 --> 08:24.560
I'm already recruiting.

08:24.560 --> 08:26.120
Ms. Lin, who are you looking for?

08:26.120 --> 08:27.270
Don't find someone who can't play.

08:27.270 --> 08:27.800
Yeah.

08:28.270 --> 08:29.480
He's very good.

08:29.680 --> 08:31.680
You've already played against him.

08:33.030 --> 08:34.030
Played against him?

08:34.030 --> 08:35.549
Wen Chengye?

08:35.549 --> 08:36.669
It can't be him, can it?

08:36.669 --> 08:38.030
How could it be him?

08:38.030 --> 08:38.870
Congratulations.

08:38.870 --> 08:39.870
You guessed it right.

08:39.870 --> 08:41.200
Didn't he insult us?

08:41.200 --> 08:42.000
Would he even come?

08:42.000 --> 08:43.240
How will we even play if he comes?

08:43.240 --> 08:44.000
Right.

08:46.000 --> 08:48.030
He hasn't agreed yet.

08:48.240 --> 08:49.750
How could a black sheep like him

08:49.750 --> 08:51.000
ever agree?

08:53.550 --> 08:55.160
If it's really Wen Chengye,

08:55.180 --> 08:56.440
maybe I could go ask him.

08:56.440 --> 08:57.360
Bro,

08:57.360 --> 09:00.080
even the teacher failed,
so why do you think you can?

09:00.080 --> 09:01.480
Out of genuine goodwill.

09:02.440 --> 09:04.270
Because I think we are
the same kind of people.

09:04.270 --> 09:05.530
We both love football.

09:09.360 --> 09:10.120
Perhaps,

09:10.480 --> 09:12.740
he might have a better chance of success.

09:25.870 --> 09:27.440
My washing machine is broken.

09:27.440 --> 09:29.120
Can I borrow yours?

09:30.120 --> 09:31.000
Come in.

09:33.200 --> 09:34.080
Thank you.

09:40.630 --> 09:42.360
This takes care of everything.

09:44.080 --> 09:45.120
I'm curious.

09:45.440 --> 09:47.440
Don't you need to sort your clothes?

09:47.790 --> 09:48.870
I don't mind.

09:50.550 --> 09:52.210
Washing will take a long time.

09:52.630 --> 09:54.020
Since we're just waiting,

09:54.020 --> 09:55.070
do you remember

09:55.120 --> 09:57.250
you promised to help with my insomnia?

09:58.320 --> 10:02.080
You really are the master
of time management, Coach.

10:02.080 --> 10:03.320
Let me help you out.

10:03.320 --> 10:04.200
Perfect.

10:04.200 --> 10:05.790
I can seize the chance to test her.

10:05.790 --> 10:06.630
No problem.

10:17.440 --> 10:18.240
All right.

10:18.480 --> 10:19.410
What's this for?

10:19.600 --> 10:21.000
While you are talking,

10:21.000 --> 10:22.630
you should avoid looking me in the eye.

10:22.630 --> 10:24.420
This will reduce your stress.

10:28.840 --> 10:30.150
You look like a pro.

10:30.150 --> 10:31.870
More professional than you claimed.

10:31.870 --> 10:34.000
I can't guarantee it will work,

10:34.000 --> 10:36.480
but at least,
I can listen to your troubles

10:36.750 --> 10:38.720
and share some simple methods

10:38.720 --> 10:40.720
on how to relieve insomnia.

10:41.480 --> 10:42.240
Okay.

10:42.720 --> 10:43.600
Let's begin.

10:44.000 --> 10:44.870
Be casual.

10:45.630 --> 10:47.510
First, let's relax.

10:47.510 --> 10:49.720
Share what's been on your mind lately.

10:51.080 --> 10:52.390
Relax?

10:53.150 --> 10:54.510
Can I use my own method?

10:55.150 --> 10:55.910
Of course.

10:59.390 --> 11:00.240
By the way,

11:01.080 --> 11:02.810
what color do you like, Ms. Lin?

11:04.550 --> 11:05.270
Color.

11:06.150 --> 11:06.910
Blue.

11:07.440 --> 11:09.000
Why ask this all of a sudden?

11:10.480 --> 11:11.870
You'll know in a bit.

11:23.120 --> 11:24.750
My way to relax is simple:

11:25.870 --> 11:26.630
drinking.

11:27.910 --> 11:29.750
This color is beautiful.

11:29.750 --> 11:30.880
What's its name?

11:30.960 --> 11:32.620
This is my impromptu special.

11:33.200 --> 11:34.390
It doesn't have a name yet.

11:34.390 --> 11:35.720
Then name it impromptu.

11:40.910 --> 11:42.360
Let's call it Secret.

11:43.080 --> 11:44.270
Secret.

11:45.360 --> 11:47.080
Seems you are very vigilant.

11:47.080 --> 11:47.910
Very apt.

11:48.550 --> 11:50.390
It suits you too.

11:51.030 --> 11:52.480
You don't mean that.

11:52.480 --> 11:53.630
Why do you think so?

11:56.030 --> 11:58.180
You had a bright future in the UK.

11:58.360 --> 12:00.220
Why did you come back so suddenly?

12:02.870 --> 12:04.480
Because of you, of course.

12:07.440 --> 12:10.770
You were a top psychology student
at Yongchuan University.

12:11.120 --> 12:11.890
Why would you be

12:11.890 --> 12:13.460
a Sports Equipment Keeper?

12:14.870 --> 12:16.970
Are you Spade Q or not?

12:17.630 --> 12:19.510
That's none of your business.

12:21.480 --> 12:22.750
Mr. Win,

12:23.320 --> 12:25.550
if you answer a question with another one,

12:25.550 --> 12:27.630
our chat won't make any progress.

12:28.630 --> 12:30.000
Dare not answer?

12:30.750 --> 12:31.670
It seems you

12:31.670 --> 12:33.670
don't want to answer this question.

12:34.030 --> 12:35.120
Isn't it obvious?

12:36.150 --> 12:37.750
Then let's change the topic.

12:37.750 --> 12:39.000
Do you like the UK?

12:39.200 --> 12:40.330
Have you been there?

12:42.840 --> 12:45.080
I was an exchange student
in London for a year.

12:45.080 --> 12:47.030
Was it a psychological institution

12:47.030 --> 12:48.320
or a university lab?

12:50.480 --> 12:51.740
Mr. Win,

12:51.910 --> 12:53.360
I think right now,

12:53.360 --> 12:55.360
we've put the cart before the horse.

13:00.790 --> 13:01.990
London is very humid.

13:02.390 --> 13:03.510
I like it a lot.

13:04.360 --> 13:05.030
And you?

13:13.220 --> 13:14.040
I hate...

13:15.720 --> 13:16.630
rainy days.

13:19.550 --> 13:21.840
What do rainy days make you feel?

13:28.870 --> 13:30.240
Maybe parting.

13:41.270 --> 13:42.600
What about you, Ms. Lin?

13:43.120 --> 13:44.380
Do you like rainy days?

13:46.150 --> 13:47.240
I quite like them.

13:47.720 --> 13:49.360
I don't have to go out on rainy days.

13:49.360 --> 13:50.870
I can stay at home alone

13:51.120 --> 13:52.670
and chat on the phone with friends.

13:52.670 --> 13:53.630
It's very cozy.

13:54.000 --> 13:55.000
Chat on the phone?

13:55.870 --> 13:57.720
Do you have many friends in the UK?

13:57.720 --> 13:58.390
It's okay.

13:58.810 --> 13:59.610
Not that many.

13:59.630 --> 14:01.120
If you really were to call,

14:01.840 --> 14:03.900
which friend in the UK would you call?

14:12.080 --> 14:13.340
The clothes are ready.

14:17.840 --> 14:20.210
I'll leave these things at your place,

14:20.360 --> 14:21.960
so they're handy for next time,

14:21.960 --> 14:23.200
if

14:23.200 --> 14:24.670
there's next time.

14:25.200 --> 14:26.440
I'm looking forward

14:27.200 --> 14:28.130
to the next time.

14:46.090 --> 14:48.430
[Hates rainy days]

14:48.450 --> 14:50.990
[Fireflies expert]

14:51.010 --> 14:53.840
[Favorite color]

14:56.180 --> 14:57.670
[Favorite color]

15:07.030 --> 15:09.170
[Class 1, Grade 12]

15:13.870 --> 15:14.630
Wen Chengye.

15:24.570 --> 15:28.110
[Class 4, Grade 12]

15:26.030 --> 15:26.870
Wen Chengye!

15:29.240 --> 15:30.240
What is it?

15:32.470 --> 15:34.600
I want to invite you
to join the football team.

15:34.600 --> 15:36.000
Sure, I agree.

15:36.720 --> 15:37.320
Wait.

15:40.550 --> 15:42.240
You agreed last time,

15:42.630 --> 15:44.030
but you still stood me up.

15:44.750 --> 15:46.810
Can you answer me seriously for once?

15:49.510 --> 15:50.320
Okay.

15:51.000 --> 15:51.800
I promise you.

15:53.550 --> 15:54.950
But I have one condition.

15:55.600 --> 15:56.360
Tell me.

15:58.720 --> 16:00.570
Be my lackey for a week.

16:00.720 --> 16:02.320
It shouldn't be hard, right?

16:07.720 --> 16:08.480
Okay.

16:08.480 --> 16:09.320
I promise you.

16:12.120 --> 16:13.270
Wait for my notice at any time.

16:13.270 --> 16:13.790
Okay.

16:13.790 --> 16:14.910
Keep your word.

16:41.270 --> 16:42.300
[Wen Chengye]

16:42.330 --> 16:43.240
[Task List]

16:43.270 --> 16:43.790
[Monday] [Breakfast: Buns, soy milk]

16:43.820 --> 16:44.300
[Break: Get warm water with my bottle]
[Afternoon: Buy soda]

16:44.330 --> 16:44.990
[from the store] [Before dismissal:
Do my homework]

16:45.010 --> 16:45.580
[Tuesday] [Breakfast: Wonton]

16:45.600 --> 16:46.180
[Break: Get warm water with my bottle]
[Afternoon: Line up in the canteen]

16:46.200 --> 16:46.680
[to get food ahead of time]
[Before dismissal: Do my homework]

16:46.700 --> 16:47.290
[Wednesday] [Breakfast: Shumai, milk]

16:47.310 --> 16:47.950
[Lunch: Buy fried noodles outside]
[Afternoon: Buy popular bread]

16:47.970 --> 16:48.530
[from the store] [Night: Cleaning duty]

16:48.560 --> 16:49.160
[Thursday] [Break: Clean the skateboard]

16:49.180 --> 16:50.160
[Lunch: Line up in the canteen to get food
ahead of time] [Before dismissal: Do]

16:50.180 --> 16:51.060
[my homework and copy down
the wrong questions in my error notebook]

16:51.080 --> 16:52.130
[Friday] [Breakfast: Wonton]

16:52.150 --> 16:52.750
[Wen Chengye]

16:52.780 --> 16:53.250
[Noon: Cleaning duty]

16:53.270 --> 16:54.000
[Afternoon: Buy sweet and spicy
potato chips from the store, and sneakers]

16:54.130 --> 16:57.400
[Wen Chengye]

16:56.270 --> 16:57.240
Besides,

16:57.550 --> 16:58.630
the tasks I give you

16:58.630 --> 17:00.490
must be completed within an hour.

17:01.120 --> 17:02.840
If you're late or don't want to do them,

17:02.840 --> 17:04.900
you'll be considered as abstaining.

17:08.880 --> 17:09.750
Okay,

17:09.750 --> 17:12.280
as long as it doesn't take up
my training time.

17:12.640 --> 17:13.260
[Fu Xinshu]

17:13.290 --> 17:14.700
[Okay, as long as it doesn't take up
my training time.]

17:34.720 --> 17:36.030
I'm so hungry.

17:36.350 --> 17:37.950
Let me order something good.

17:42.350 --> 17:43.960
Balanced nutrition.

17:49.400 --> 17:50.590
The guy upstairs

17:50.590 --> 17:52.270
is weird every day.

17:58.270 --> 18:00.230
He came to Hongjing alone,

18:00.400 --> 18:01.730
suffers from insomnia,

18:02.110 --> 18:03.510
and exiles himself.

18:04.590 --> 18:06.510
He must have gone through

18:06.510 --> 18:07.920
something in the UK.

18:24.110 --> 18:24.880
Ms. Lin,

18:25.160 --> 18:26.330
your milk tea is here.

18:26.330 --> 18:27.750
The gate is open for you.

18:27.750 --> 18:28.810
Please bring it up.

18:33.070 --> 18:34.070
Thank you.

18:34.440 --> 18:36.800
You're welcome. Enjoy your meal.

18:36.830 --> 18:38.290
Thanks for your hard work.

18:44.880 --> 18:46.160
Fruits and ice cream are here.

18:46.160 --> 18:47.400
Are you coming down to get them,
or should I bring them up?

18:47.400 --> 18:48.600
Please bring them up.

19:08.440 --> 19:09.790
Ms. Lin, your delivery is here.

19:09.790 --> 19:10.830
Please open the door.

19:10.830 --> 19:11.920
Coming.

19:13.070 --> 19:14.590
River snail rice noodles,
river snail rice noodles.

19:14.590 --> 19:15.270
Your food delivery.

19:15.270 --> 19:16.790
Thanks for your hard work.

19:25.880 --> 19:27.230
Did I...

19:27.510 --> 19:28.350
disturb you?

19:31.440 --> 19:32.070
Perfect timing.

19:32.070 --> 19:33.550
I ordered a lot of food.

19:33.550 --> 19:36.150
Why don't we have
late-night snacks together?

19:46.560 --> 19:48.690
[Bug Super Encyclopedia]

20:09.680 --> 20:11.200
Such a strong taste.

20:15.550 --> 20:17.130
I'll bear the pain of parting with it.

20:17.130 --> 20:17.980
It's yours.

20:22.270 --> 20:23.790
Ms. Lin, at night, please

20:23.790 --> 20:25.070
keep your voice down.

20:25.320 --> 20:26.950
Your upstairs neighbor
suffers from insomnia.

20:26.950 --> 20:28.440
What a coincidence.

20:28.440 --> 20:30.030
River snail rice noodles cure insomnia.

20:30.030 --> 20:30.960
Didn't you know?

20:31.240 --> 20:32.270
Just fooling him.

20:34.400 --> 20:36.450
This kind of abnormal junk food...

20:36.640 --> 20:38.000
Looking down on junk food

20:38.000 --> 20:39.400
means looking down on me.

20:39.590 --> 20:41.030
Psychologically speaking,

20:41.030 --> 20:42.510
giving up the standard answer

20:42.510 --> 20:44.200
and becoming an abnormal you

20:44.200 --> 20:46.530
are often the beginning of self-healing.

20:47.200 --> 20:47.930
Give it a try.

20:52.440 --> 20:54.950
I even believe it myself.

20:55.070 --> 20:56.510
Give myself a like.

20:56.510 --> 20:57.400
Or maybe,

20:57.750 --> 20:58.880
I'll give it a try?

21:04.680 --> 21:06.160
He's fallen for it.

21:06.750 --> 21:07.500
Will...

21:07.920 --> 21:09.920
will this work?

21:13.400 --> 21:15.510
How is it? Delicious, right?

21:16.160 --> 21:17.090
Let me try again.

21:21.240 --> 21:22.110
Wait a minute.

21:22.510 --> 21:24.270
You have to poke the egg down

21:24.270 --> 21:25.400
into the broth.

21:25.400 --> 21:27.600
Let it soak up the broth to make it tasty.

21:28.400 --> 21:30.830
So many rules
just to eat river snail rice noodles.

21:30.830 --> 21:31.720
Yes, right.

21:31.720 --> 21:32.780
Press it down more.

21:36.000 --> 21:37.750
You really should thank me.

21:37.750 --> 21:40.410
I've brought you
to taste something delicious.

21:45.830 --> 21:47.890
I can tell you don't know how to eat it.

21:52.220 --> 21:54.350
That's not how you eat these noodles.

21:54.370 --> 21:55.680
You have to slurp them

21:55.680 --> 21:56.960
to get the broth.

21:56.960 --> 21:58.020
Slurp like this...

22:02.270 --> 22:03.070
You go ahead.

22:03.680 --> 22:04.610
Eat it yourself.

22:05.960 --> 22:07.160
Why are you so mean?

22:23.400 --> 22:25.930
Why are the river snail rice noodles
so salty?

23:31.070 --> 23:33.470
Let's see what you have to say
for yourself.

23:42.440 --> 23:44.550
Look what time it is,
and you're just heading out.

23:44.550 --> 23:46.400
You really can eat and sleep.

23:48.160 --> 23:48.830
Is he here

23:48.830 --> 23:50.720
-to take revenge on me?
-Good morning.

23:50.720 --> 23:51.590
Morning.

23:53.200 --> 23:54.800
How did you sleep last night?

23:55.590 --> 23:56.590
What do you think?

23:56.680 --> 23:58.410
He has such heavy dark circles.

23:58.680 --> 24:00.480
Looks like he didn't sleep well.

24:01.270 --> 24:02.130
You tricked me.

24:02.960 --> 24:05.030
The theory
about changing oneself is right,

24:05.030 --> 24:06.890
but the river snail rice noodles

24:07.030 --> 24:08.830
were indeed a bit too salty for you.

24:08.830 --> 24:09.590
So?

24:09.590 --> 24:10.440
Yeah.

24:10.790 --> 24:11.850
I was tricking you.

24:12.440 --> 24:14.370
It is impolite not to reciprocate.

24:14.750 --> 24:16.510
What did you buy for breakfast, Coach?

24:16.510 --> 24:17.640
Steamed rice cakes?

24:20.550 --> 24:22.310
Trying to get revenge on me

24:22.310 --> 24:23.730
won't be that easy.

24:24.160 --> 24:25.160
Thanks.

24:25.160 --> 24:26.310
I'm running late.

24:26.960 --> 24:27.660
I...

24:28.160 --> 24:30.030
I've never seen anyone like you.

24:32.590 --> 24:33.680
Hello.

24:33.360 --> 24:39.270
[Wen Chengye]
[Buy breakfast before school]

24:33.700 --> 24:35.400
-The first task...
-Beef croissant, with 2 more pickles.

24:35.400 --> 24:36.480
Buy breakfast before school.

24:36.480 --> 24:37.750
Hot latte.

24:37.750 --> 24:39.400
Swap the milk for low-fat milk, please.

24:39.400 --> 24:41.200
Okay. That'll be 30. Scan here.

24:41.200 --> 24:41.830
Okay.

24:44.110 --> 24:46.030
Okay, thanks.

25:06.000 --> 25:07.060
Finished writing?

25:20.800 --> 25:24.810
[Wen Chengye]

25:21.240 --> 25:22.480
Before class tomorrow,

25:22.480 --> 25:25.810
organize today's notes
for all subjects and give them to me.

25:28.640 --> 25:29.510
Let's go eat.

25:29.510 --> 25:31.240
-Let's go.
-Stop sleeping.

25:31.880 --> 25:33.310
Fu, let's go eat.

25:33.310 --> 25:34.270
What time is it?

25:34.270 --> 25:35.480
Mealtime.

25:35.480 --> 25:36.480
It's mealtime?

25:39.930 --> 25:42.390
[Wen Chengye]

25:40.000 --> 25:42.000
Buy a pretzel bun for my meal,

25:42.000 --> 25:43.060
cheese-flavored.

25:54.260 --> 25:55.460
The bread you wanted.

26:08.570 --> 26:15.110
[Wen Chengye]

26:11.090 --> 26:14.090
Come to my class
and clean the classroom after school.

26:15.680 --> 26:16.510
Wen Chengye.

26:16.510 --> 26:17.510
I'm leaving.

26:17.510 --> 26:18.200
Bye-bye.

27:25.880 --> 27:27.940
That's for tricking me this morning.

27:32.110 --> 27:34.370
Why are you drinking alone here, Ms. Lin?

27:35.110 --> 27:36.570
Is something on your mind?

27:39.070 --> 27:41.530
Coach Wang, you're here
to run into me again.

27:41.640 --> 27:42.720
I'm telling you,

27:42.720 --> 27:45.240
the sausages at this supermarket
are super delicious.

27:45.240 --> 27:46.790
They're limited to 10 a day.

27:47.400 --> 27:49.060
I'm waiting for the sausages.

27:49.830 --> 27:50.550
Okay.

27:50.550 --> 27:51.880
The sausages are ready.

27:55.000 --> 27:56.760
Don't take my sausage.

27:56.920 --> 27:59.780
Didn't you take
my steamed rice cakes this morning?

28:25.400 --> 28:26.790
So messy.

28:30.480 --> 28:31.790
Does it really taste good that way?

28:31.790 --> 28:34.390
If you want some,
go line up and buy it yourself.

28:35.590 --> 28:36.400
By the way,

28:36.640 --> 28:37.880
Fu Xinshu told me

28:37.880 --> 28:39.720
he wanted to handle Wen Chengye himself.

28:39.720 --> 28:40.790
You're the supervisor,

28:40.790 --> 28:42.650
but you're not stepping in at all?

28:44.510 --> 28:46.970
You were also the one
who let Chen Weidong go.

28:47.720 --> 28:48.590
You didn't promise

28:48.590 --> 28:50.240
to stay and teach them forever, either.

28:50.240 --> 28:52.110
Let's not guilt-trip each other.

28:59.000 --> 29:00.260
Have you noticed that,

29:00.350 --> 29:01.750
compared to the team,

29:02.270 --> 29:03.310
Wen Chengye

29:03.310 --> 29:05.840
seems to pay a bit more attention
to Fu Xinshu?

29:07.550 --> 29:09.750
I didn't expect you, who usually

29:09.750 --> 29:11.550
just slack off and eat snacks,

29:12.030 --> 29:12.830
to have observed everything on the pitch

29:12.830 --> 29:14.480
so clearly.

29:15.270 --> 29:16.000
No way,

29:16.000 --> 29:17.330
you noticed it long ago?

29:19.030 --> 29:20.240
No need to worship me.

29:26.000 --> 29:28.260
I don't worship men who only drink water.

29:42.000 --> 29:42.880
Fu Xinshu.

29:53.400 --> 29:54.660
The retros you wanted.

29:54.720 --> 29:56.000
The shoes cost 1,680.

29:56.310 --> 29:57.310
There's 320 left.

29:58.920 --> 30:00.180
You have one last task.

30:01.510 --> 30:02.110
What is it?

30:05.480 --> 30:06.480
It's very simple.

30:10.750 --> 30:12.170
Help me put the shoes on.

30:16.230 --> 30:16.920
Why?

30:16.920 --> 30:18.580
You don't even want to do this?

30:28.310 --> 30:29.770
Queuing to buy breakfast,

30:30.480 --> 30:32.320
doing homework, cleaning up,

30:32.510 --> 30:33.770
and buying the retros.

30:34.400 --> 30:36.060
I did all the things you asked.

30:36.590 --> 30:38.120
As for what you promised me,

30:38.400 --> 30:40.060
shouldn't you keep your word?

30:41.200 --> 30:43.530
I don't remember promising you anything.

30:44.350 --> 30:46.010
Wen Chengye, I'll beat you up!

30:46.110 --> 30:46.550
Boss!

30:48.350 --> 30:49.400
Calm down!

30:49.400 --> 30:51.400
If you get another penalty,
you'll be expelled!

30:51.400 --> 30:52.720
To hell with the penalty!

30:52.720 --> 30:53.350
So what?

30:53.350 --> 30:55.110
He bullied you.
Can't I beat him up for you?

30:55.110 --> 30:57.710
He's happier than anyone
when he provokes you.

31:32.720 --> 31:34.120
We'll find someone else.

31:36.590 --> 31:37.200
Let's go.

31:46.160 --> 31:47.690
It's nice to have brothers.

31:48.260 --> 31:49.920
No wonder you forgot about me.

31:57.000 --> 31:59.730
Actually, I'm willing
to join the football team.

32:01.690 --> 32:04.200
But playing football
with those weaker than me

32:04.200 --> 32:05.240
is very boring.

32:05.920 --> 32:07.400
You really think
I can't deal with you, right?

32:07.400 --> 32:08.060
Speak.

32:08.310 --> 32:09.240
What do you want?

32:09.510 --> 32:10.720
In this monthly exam,

32:10.720 --> 32:12.400
if your English score is higher than mine,

32:12.400 --> 32:13.930
I'll admit you're not weak,

32:14.680 --> 32:16.480
and I'll join the football team.

32:17.720 --> 32:18.590
Let's go, Fu.

32:18.720 --> 32:19.640
He's messing with you.

32:19.640 --> 32:20.700
Let's go. Let's go.

32:21.310 --> 32:23.240
It seems your passion for football

32:24.440 --> 32:25.440
is just a joke.

32:34.510 --> 32:35.370
Let's compete.

32:36.270 --> 32:37.600
I will compete with you.

32:47.150 --> 32:51.570
[Sports Equipment Room]

32:49.000 --> 32:49.920
Ms. Lin,

32:49.920 --> 32:50.750
do you think Fu Xinshu

32:50.750 --> 32:51.720
is stupid?

32:51.720 --> 32:52.920
Wen Chengye

32:52.950 --> 32:54.680
definitely did it on purpose.

32:54.880 --> 32:56.000
He knows Fu Xinshu's

32:56.000 --> 32:57.160
English is bad.

32:57.160 --> 32:58.070
Right?

32:58.070 --> 32:59.510
I really can't let this go.

32:59.510 --> 33:00.200
I beg you...

33:00.200 --> 33:01.680
-I'll do it.
-I'll do it.

33:08.680 --> 33:09.510
Ms. Lin,

33:09.720 --> 33:10.880
how about...

33:12.070 --> 33:14.160
I lend you my novel for a couple of days?

33:14.160 --> 33:14.960
Ms. Lin,

33:14.960 --> 33:16.310
I'll come to the equipment room every day

33:16.310 --> 33:17.110
to help you clean up.

33:17.110 --> 33:18.000
Ms. Lin,

33:18.000 --> 33:19.160
you were the top scorer in liberal arts
in the college entrance exam,

33:19.160 --> 33:20.200
published 6 SCI papers,

33:20.200 --> 33:22.440
and won the first-class scholarship
for 7 consecutive years.

33:22.440 --> 33:23.000
Yes.

33:23.000 --> 33:24.350
Ms. Lin, weren't you a top student?

33:24.350 --> 33:25.410
You must have a way.

33:25.790 --> 33:27.070
Please help Fu Xinshu.

33:27.070 --> 33:28.240
Count these volleyballs.

33:28.240 --> 33:28.830
Okay.

33:32.550 --> 33:33.410
What about you?

33:33.790 --> 33:34.790
What do you think?

33:39.110 --> 33:40.050
Ms. Lin,

33:40.160 --> 33:41.000
I want to win.

33:45.600 --> 33:47.060
You may not know,

33:47.270 --> 33:48.440
but the feeling of being looked down upon

33:48.440 --> 33:49.770
is really awful.

33:50.110 --> 33:51.370
I just want to win once.

33:51.590 --> 33:53.250
I want him to look me in the eye.

33:54.390 --> 33:55.040
Okay,

33:55.350 --> 33:56.200
then win once.

34:00.680 --> 34:01.400
But Ms. Lin,

34:01.400 --> 34:02.400
I always

34:02.400 --> 34:04.000
rank dead last in English.

34:04.200 --> 34:05.160
I know.

34:05.640 --> 34:06.450
So,

34:06.680 --> 34:09.110
working hard alone is useless.

34:10.880 --> 34:11.710
Are you guys

34:12.230 --> 34:14.440
ready to put in the effort
for him together?

34:14.440 --> 34:16.000
-We're ready, Ms. Lin.
-We're ready, Ms. Lin.

34:16.000 --> 34:16.480
Okay,

34:16.920 --> 34:18.600
from now on,

34:18.710 --> 34:20.320
let's prepare for
the crash course together.

34:20.320 --> 34:21.719
Okay, thank you, Ms. Lin.

34:22.550 --> 34:23.670
Crash course?

34:24.150 --> 34:24.960
What's that?

34:25.110 --> 34:26.110
-Can it work?
-Yeah.

34:26.110 --> 34:26.920
What crash course?

34:26.920 --> 34:28.230
Don't worry.

34:28.260 --> 34:29.480
When it comes to studying,

34:29.480 --> 34:31.070
I always win beautifully.

34:32.320 --> 34:32.710
Okay.

34:42.179 --> 34:43.010
Fu,

34:43.480 --> 34:45.409
I heard you made a bet with Wen Chengye

34:45.409 --> 34:46.600
on English.

34:46.670 --> 34:47.760
Are you out of your mind?

34:47.760 --> 34:48.630
Exactly.

34:48.880 --> 34:51.630
That guy picked what Fu is worst at.

34:52.000 --> 34:52.630
Why are you doing this?

34:52.630 --> 34:53.909
Asking to be humiliated?

34:53.909 --> 34:54.940
You talk too much.

34:55.480 --> 34:57.230
We have a secret weapon.

34:58.630 --> 34:59.760
What secret weapon?

35:01.320 --> 35:02.980
Here comes the secret weapon.

35:03.030 --> 35:03.670
Coach,

35:04.190 --> 35:06.320
may I borrow your players for a moment?

35:09.920 --> 35:10.760
Boys,

35:10.760 --> 35:11.820
pause for a moment.

35:12.360 --> 35:12.960
Ms. Lin.

35:12.960 --> 35:14.820
-Hello, Ms. Lin.
-Hello, Ms. Lin.

35:16.280 --> 35:17.070
Ms. Lin,

35:17.070 --> 35:18.360
what did you hand out?

35:18.360 --> 35:19.710
-It's in English.
-Thank you.

35:19.710 --> 35:20.920
What is this?

35:22.880 --> 35:24.550
What's all this?

35:24.550 --> 35:26.320
What are you up to, Ms. Lin?

35:26.320 --> 35:27.280
W...

35:27.800 --> 35:28.920
You all should know

35:28.920 --> 35:29.670
that your captain

35:29.670 --> 35:31.740
made a bet with Wen Chengye, right?

35:32.630 --> 35:34.660
Ms. Lin, skip the prologue.

35:34.760 --> 35:36.490
Just get straight to the point.

35:38.230 --> 35:39.630
The cards in your hands

35:39.630 --> 35:42.920
contain the key points
for this monthly exam that I prepared.

35:42.920 --> 35:44.360
I hope that from now on,

35:44.360 --> 35:45.960
every day and every moment,

35:45.960 --> 35:48.030
you will be in Fu Xinshu's ear,

35:48.030 --> 35:49.320
spelling,

35:49.320 --> 35:50.960
reading, and reciting loudly,

35:50.960 --> 35:52.360
until he memorizes them.

35:52.710 --> 35:53.440
This...

35:53.880 --> 35:54.630
Ms. Lin,

35:55.280 --> 35:57.280
this guy hasn't even
figured them out himself.

35:57.280 --> 35:58.800
How can he teach others?

35:58.800 --> 35:59.800
Let me tell you,

35:59.800 --> 36:01.760
I can memorize them in minutes.

36:01.760 --> 36:02.800
Stop bragging.

36:02.800 --> 36:03.840
How about this?

36:03.840 --> 36:06.540
From today
until the end of the monthly exam,

36:06.800 --> 36:08.710
we can only communicate in English.

36:08.710 --> 36:10.510
Whoever breaks the rule is a coward.

36:10.510 --> 36:11.880
-Okay.
-Good idea.

36:12.880 --> 36:14.250
All right, guys.

36:14.630 --> 36:16.190
Warm-up is over.

36:16.960 --> 36:17.960
We're moving on

36:17.960 --> 36:19.820
to the competitive drills, okay?

36:20.150 --> 36:22.000
What is he saying?

36:23.070 --> 36:24.230
I don't understand.

36:24.320 --> 36:25.710
-What? What?
-What is the coach talking about?

36:25.710 --> 36:26.440
-I don't understand.
-Me neither.

36:26.440 --> 36:28.280
Speaking English already?

36:28.710 --> 36:30.280
Very cooperative.

36:30.280 --> 36:32.630
-What is he mumbling about?
-I don't understand.

36:32.630 --> 36:33.230
Let's go.

36:33.230 --> 36:34.760
Go! Go! Go!

36:34.760 --> 36:36.230
Let's go, brothers!

36:37.440 --> 36:37.960
Go.

36:38.360 --> 36:39.760
Go! Go! Go!

36:42.480 --> 36:44.190
What did you just say?

36:46.880 --> 36:47.550
Qin Ao, hurry up.

36:47.550 --> 36:48.760
Your English is pretty good.

36:48.760 --> 36:49.960
Why don't you join in?

36:50.280 --> 36:51.230
I'm stupid.

36:52.400 --> 36:53.630
-Come on.
-Stand still. Stand still.

36:53.630 --> 36:55.360
Can you all understand what I wrote?

36:55.360 --> 36:56.480
-Yes.
-Yes.

36:56.480 --> 36:57.550
-Yes, I understand.
-Really?

36:57.550 --> 36:59.920
I'm amazing.

37:05.990 --> 37:07.310
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

37:08.400 --> 37:09.890
♪ Because you're with me ♪

37:12.640 --> 37:14.080
♪ The light shimmers ♪

37:15.340 --> 37:16.660
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

37:18.250 --> 37:19.370
♪ Running towards you ♪

37:20.270 --> 37:21.530
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪

37:25.310 --> 37:26.550
♪ Walk side by side ♪

37:27.110 --> 37:29.240
♪ Become ourselves ♪

37:31.030 --> 37:33.610
♪ We get closer in a storm ♪
